{"id": "pos008", "name": "Audio_NMobile_693_08_14", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Restaurant_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "It's been a while since we three had dinner together. I reserve this table a whole week in advance just for this occasion... This is \"L'Atelier de Charlotte\", Node 08's most renowned 5-Star Buffet. Delicacies from all across the world can be found here. \nIt's on me tonight. Eat whatever you desire.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Wow, it must be quite expensive here. Are you alright with that?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma's making her debut tomorrow. You've been working really hard as well lately, haven't you? If it's for you guys, I said it's money well spent. No need to be concerned about it.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You're being considerate for once, good.\nThose people at Mono really are a pain in the neck. It's truly exhausting to deal with them... Aroma, you must be hungry too, right? Don't go easy on his wallet.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Hungry! Hungry!</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "...... Ok.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "So you're back? Let's not wait for you sister and dig in right now.\n... What's with the tiny portions? Is that enough for you?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Where's sister?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I just saw her walked pass here. She's probably waiting in line for the grilled meats. The ribs there are the signature dish of this restaurant, so there's always a long line. I highly recommend you go try it out yourself later.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Sure...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... A, Aroma, about that incident a few days ago... I'm sorry! I was just too drunk that day.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I was feeling really frustrated that day. The higher-ups have no idea about the importance of that technology... All in all, I got yell at by my superiors. On my way home, I decided to make a detour and visit a bar. I may had too many drinks there... Did I... I didn't do anything terrible to you, did I?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Noah... so... you don't remember anything?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I can only recall bits and pieces... I yelled at you, and I think I pushed you as well... I am so sorry!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... It was much more than just that...</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Hm? What?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... No, nothing...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No matter what, let me apologize for what I did. I will never do that again!\nDoes Helena know about this? I will have to apologize to her as well.\n\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"4.0\">...... NO!</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Other Diners"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Umm. Sorry for disturbing everyone... We're fine.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">Keep your voice down... Why did you shout all of a sudden?</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "You can't... let sister know about it.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah, you said you will never do it again. I believe you... Don't tell sister anything about this incident...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Understood. I will not talk about it.\nThank you for your forgiveness, Aroma.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "It's ok. I know that your job is tough...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Thank you so much...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Can you let go of me now...?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "AH! I'm so sorry... I'll go grab a cold drink to calm myself down. Aroma, what would you like to drink?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I don't know what options are there... Let me go get it.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Got it. Then get me a glass of orange juice with extra ice.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Note: Orange juice, more ice!</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "OK.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Sniffing", "Smells hand"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... Did I rush it? That's not good... Hehehe.</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Restaurant_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "3人で外食をするのは久しぶりだからね。\n1週間前からレストランを予約していたんだよ。\nこのお店「L'Atelier de Charlotte」はね、Node08で一番有名な5つ星ビュッフェなんだ。\n今日は僕がごちそうするから、好きなだけ食べてね。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "まあ、ここお高いんじゃない？\n本当に大丈夫なの？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "明日はAromaちゃんのデビューだからね。\nずっと頑張ってきたけど、最近は特に大変だったんじゃないかい？\n君たちのためなら、このくらいどうってことないよ。\n気にしないで。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あら、あなたにしては気が利くじゃない。\nMONOの人たちってば、本当面倒くさいのよ。\n疲れるったらありゃしない……\nAromaもお腹すいたでしょ？遠慮せずに食べなさい。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>お腹ペコペコ！ペコペコ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……うん。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aromaちゃん早いね。\nHelenaのことは気にしなくていいから先に食べてていいよ。\n……それしか取らなかったのかい？足りないだろう？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……お姉ちゃんは……？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "さっき見かけたけど、まだ料理の所に並んでるんじゃないかな？\nここのリブはとても人気で、すごく並ぶから。\nAromaちゃんもあとで食べてみるといいよ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……A、Aromaちゃん、この前のことだけど……本当に申し訳ない！\n飲み過ぎて……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あの日は本当に気分が落ち込んでいたんだ。\n上司はあの技術の重要性について何も分かってない……\n色々言われて、家に帰る前にバーで飲みすぎちゃって……僕……君になにかしたりしてないよね？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……Noahさん……何も、覚えてない、の？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ほんの少ししか覚えてないんだ……\n確か、僕は君に向かって何か叫んで、君を突き飛ばしたよね……\n本当に悪かった！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……そ、それだけじゃない……</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "え？なんて？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……なんでも…ない……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "とにかく、本当に悪かったと思ってるんだ。\nごめんね、Aromaちゃん。\nもう二度とあんなことしない。\nHelenaはこのこと知ってる？\nHelenaにも謝らないと。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"4.0\">……ダメ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["他の客"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あっ……と……お騒がせして申し訳ありません……何でもないので。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">落ち着いて……急に大声を出してどうしたんだい？</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃんには……言っちゃダメ。……絶対に。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noahさんがもうしないって言うなら、信じるから……だから、お姉ちゃんには何も言わないで……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……分かった。Helenaには言わないよ。\n分かってくれてありがとう……Aromaちゃん。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……お仕事大変なのは分かってるから……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "本当に、ありがとう……Aromaちゃん。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……手、放して……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "おっと！ごめんごめん……\n僕は冷たいドリンクでも取りに行くよ。\nAromaちゃんは何か飲む？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "何があるのか分からないから……私が取りに行く。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……分かったよ。\nじゃあ、オレンジジュースをお願いしてもいいかな？\n氷多めで。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>メモ：オレンジジュース 氷多メ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……うん。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Sniffing", "手の匂いを嗅ぐ"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……少し急ぎすぎたかな？ダメダメ……ふふっ</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Restaurant_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好久沒有三個人一起出來吃飯了，我特別提早一週訂位……這間「L'Atelier de Charlotte」是 Node 08 最有名的五星級 Buffet，什麼山珍海味都有。\n來，我買單，想吃什麼儘管去拿。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "哇，這裡不便宜吧？你沒問題嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma 明天就要出道了，妳這陣子也很辛苦吧？為了你們這點錢花得太值得了，別在意。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "算你有良心。\n單聲的人有夠難搞，真的累死我了……Aroma 也餓了吧？別對他客氣喔。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>餓了！餓了！</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "回來啦？別等妳姊了，快開動吧。\n……怎麼只拿這一點？夠吃嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……姊姊呢？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "剛剛看她路過，應該在排餐區等。\n那裡的肋排是這間店的招牌菜，總是大排長龍，推薦妳等等也去吃吃看。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……A、Aroma，前幾天那件事……對不起！我那天喝得太醉了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "那天真的很沮喪，上面根本不懂那項技術的重要性……總之被狠狠吼了一頓，回家前繞去酒吧喝多了……我應該……沒有對妳做什麼過份的事吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……Noah ……不記得了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "只有一點點印象……我對妳大叫，好像還推了妳一把……真的很抱歉！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……不只這樣……</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯？什麼？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……不，沒……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "無論如何，真的很對不起！我不會再犯了。\nHelena 知道這件事嗎？我也得和她道歉才行。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"4.0\">……不行！</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["全場"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "呃，抱歉打擾大家……我們沒事。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">小聲一點……怎麼突然大叫？</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不能讓……姊姊知道。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 說了不會再犯，我相信你……不要跟姊姊說這件事……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我知道了，我不會說的。\n謝謝妳的諒解，Aroma。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不，我知道你工作很辛苦……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "真的很謝謝妳……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……手可以放開了嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "啊！抱歉抱歉……我去拿杯涼的冷靜一下。Aroma 想喝什麼？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我不知道有哪些喝的……我去拿吧。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……好，麻煩幫我拿杯柳橙汁，冰塊加多一些。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>備忘：柳橙汁，冰塊加量！</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Sniffing", "聞手"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……太急了嗎？不行呢……呵呵。</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Restaurant_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "오랜만에 우리 세 사람의 외식을 위해, 특별히 일주일 전에 예약했어. 여기 「L'Atelier de Charlotte」는 Node 08에서 제일 유명한 5성급 Buffet 야. 모든 종류의 음식들이 다 있어.\n자, 내가 낼 테니깐 마음껏 가져다 먹도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "우와! 여기 꽤 비쌀 텐데. 괜찮겠어?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "내일이 바로 Aroma가 데뷔하는 날이잖아. 너도 그동안 고생 많았지? 그에 대한 보상이라 생각하고 사양 말고 먹도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "얼레? 그래도 양심은 있는 사람이었네?\n모노 사람들 상대하는 게 여간 쉬운 게 아니더라고. 정말 피곤해 죽는 줄 알았어.... Aroma도 배고프지? 괜히 미안해하지 말고 마음껏 먹도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>배고프다! 배고프다!</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……응\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": " 왔구나? 언니 기다리지 말고 먼저 먹도록 해.\n……왜 이렇게 조금만 가져왔어?\n부족하지 않니?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……언니는요?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "방금 지나가는 거 보긴 봤는데, 아마도 줄 서러 간 것 같아. 여기 갈비가 이 식당의 간판 음식이거든. 그래서인지 사람들이 항상 줄을 서있어. 너도 조금 이따가 가서 먹어보렴.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……A、Aroma, 며칠 전에 그 일... 정말 미안하다! 내가 그날 너무 취했었나봐.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그날 정말 너무 힘들었어. 상부에서는 그 기술의 중요성을 제대로 알아주지 않아.... 돌아오는 건 흥분한 그들의 고함 소리 뿐.... 결국 집에 들어가기 전에 한 잔만 마신다는 것이 나도 모르게 그만.... 혹시... 내가 집에 돌아와서.... 뭔가 심한 짓 같은 거 하지 않았지?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……Noah 씨 …… 기억 안나세요?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "얼핏 기억나는 것도 있지만…… 너한테 큰 소리를 지르고 밀치고 그랬던 것 같은데.... 저, 정말 미안하다!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……그것 뿐만이 아닌데……</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "응? 뭐라고?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……아니, 아무것도 아니에요……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "뭐가 어찌 됐든, 정말 너무 미안하구나! 다시는 그러지 않을게. Helena도 이 일 알고 있니? Helena에게도 제대로 사과하도록 할게.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"4.0\">……안돼요!</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["손님들"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아, 죄송합니다 여러분.... 아무 일도 아닙니다.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">조용히 말해야지……왜 갑자기 큰 소리를.</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "절대로……언니가 알게 해선 안돼요.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 씨가 다시는 안 그러겠다고 하셨으니깐... 믿을게요. 그리고 언니한테는 말하지 마세요....\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "…네 말대로 할게. 절대로 말 안 할게. 용서해줘서 고맙구나, Aroma.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아니에요. 일 때문에 힘드신 거 저도 아니깐....\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "정말.... 고맙구나……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……저……손좀......\n\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아! 미안 미안....! 난 잠깐 차가운 마실 것 좀 가지러 갈 건데, Aroma는 뭐 마실래?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "뭐가 있는지 저도 잘.... 그냥 제가 가서 가져올게요.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……그래.\n그럼 오렌지주스 좀 가져다줄래? \n얼음 듬뿍 넣어서.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>메모: 오렌지주스, 얼음 듬뿍!</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "....네.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Sniffing", "손 냄새를 맡는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……너무 조급했나? 못 참겠어... 후우...</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Restaurant_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好久沒有三個人一起出來吃飯了，我特別提早一週訂位……這間「L'Atelier de Charlotte」是 Node 08 最有名的五星級 Buffet，什麼山珍海味都有。\n來，我買單，想吃什麼儘管去拿。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "哇，這裡不便宜吧？你沒問題嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma 明天就要出道了，妳這陣子也很辛苦吧？為了你們這點錢花得太值得了，別在意。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "算你有良心。\n單聲的人有夠難搞，真的累死我了……Aroma 也餓了吧？別對他客氣喔。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>餓了！餓了！</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "回來啦？別等妳姊了，快開動吧。\n……怎麼只拿這一點？夠吃嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……姊姊呢？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "剛剛看她路過，應該在排餐區等。\n那裡的肋排是這間店的招牌菜，總是大排長龍，推薦妳等等也去吃吃看。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……A、Aroma，前幾天那件事……對不起！我那天喝得太醉了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "那天真的很沮喪，上面根本不懂那項技術的重要性……總之被狠狠吼了一頓，回家前繞去酒吧喝多了……我應該……沒有對妳做什麼過份的事吧？\n"}, {"id": 19